# Implementation Plan - Portfolio Overhaul

# Goal Description
Rebuild the entire portfolio site to be "creative, attractive, and captivating". The current design is considered boring. The new design will prioritize visual excellence, premium aesthetics (glassmorphism, vibrant gradients, animations), and a dynamic user experience.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is a complete visual overhaul. The existing "boring" styles will be replaced.

## Proposed Changes

### Design System (Global)
-   **Theme**: Modern "Dark Premium" aesthetic. Deep background colors (slate/zinc/black) with vibrant accents (cyan/purple/blue) and glassmorphism effects.
-   **Typography**: Use `Inter` and `Outfit` via Google Fonts.
-   **Animations**: `framer-motion` for scroll reveals, hero entrance, and hover interactions.

