## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
-   Run `npm run build` to ensure no build errors.
-   Run `npm run lint` to enforce code quality.
-   Run `npm test` (if applicable) to check basic component rendering.

### Manual Verification
-   **Visual Check**: Build the site locally and inspect every section for "wow" factor, spacing, and responsiveness.
-   **Interaction Check**: Test all links, buttons, and form inputs.
-   **Mobile Check**: Resize browser to mobile width to verify responsive menu and layout.
